config BR2_PACKAGE_KSZ_PTP_STACK
	bool "Microchip PTP Stack"
	help
	  Microchip PTP Stack.

	  This package builds and installs the userspace 'ptp_stack'
	  command. It is up to the user to ensure that the kernel
	  configuration has all suitable options enabled to allow a
	  proper operation of 'ptp_stack'.

